    "body":  "Description: The vision requires \"electronic signatures, approvals, and justifications\". Automated parsing isn\u0027t enough; a human manager must often validate the evidence.\n\nAcceptance Criteria:\n\n[ ] Add a \"Status\" field to User Qualifications (Pending, Approved, Rejected).\n[ ] Create a UI for Managers to view \"Pending Approvals\".\n[ ] When a Manager clicks \"Approve\", require them to \"Sign\" (re-enter password or type full name) to generate a digital signature record.\n[ ] Store the digital signature hash with the approval record.\n\nContext for Copilot:\n\nStart with a simple \"Type name to sign\" mechanism.\nEnsure the backend verifies the current user has \"Manager\" permissions before accepting the approval.",
